{
  "stem": "14091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And I asked her if she could point-- if she would know which way Lapuszyno is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "She just pointed which direction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "And I start going this direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I tried as much as possible to always be in the ravines or near the wood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "I wouldn't be spotted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I walked-- it was a whole night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And I still walked, and walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "And I walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "And then it was day, and I still walked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "And it was, apparently, in the late, late afternoon that I suddenly arrived to that river that I recognized.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "And looking over that river, I recognized the house of the Bielewicz house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "And I knew that I'm very close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Before that, I was so excited that I went on to main road.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "On the main road was a man in a wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "And he caught me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "And it was so close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "And he caught me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "And he put me in-- in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "He was really drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "And he thought he really find the biggest find he could Because anybody who could produce a Jew would get paid, and especially paid with salt.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 121,
      "text": "Salt was a very, very expensive-- and a very-- you couldn't get it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 122,
      "text": "And he thought that he's going to get quite a bit, because he asked me my name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "I thought, if I will tell him my name, because of my parents that he would maybe let me go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "Because my parents were friends with many, many gentiles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "And my father was a merchant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "And he had to do business with many of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "I thought, if I'm going to say that my name is Cymer, my father Shmuel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "But, apparently, this made him even happier.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
